'''Alfie Curtis''' ([[July 28]], [[1930s|1930]]<ref name="Emmy news" />&ndash;[[November 30]], [[2017]]) was an actor who portrayed [[Doctor|Dr.]] [[Cornelius Evazan]] in [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']].<ref name="Evazan in the Databank">{{DB|character|doctorevazan|Evazan, Doctor}}</ref>

Alfie is credited by [[John Mollo]] as portraying a 'grubby human' in [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']] as documented in the [[1979]] book ''[[The Art of Star Wars Episode IV: A New Hope|The Art of Star Wars]]''.<ref name="TAoSW">[[The Art of Star Wars Episode IV: A New Hope|''The Art of Star Wars'']] {{C|page 60}}</ref>

